extended_tweet.full_text: Want to help keep voters in line at the polls? Want to report a long line at a poling place so we can get pizza delivered to the voters? I just donated to @pizzatothepolls! You can give (or report a long line) today at https://t.co/tpMGkcGqb6

unwound.title: Pizza to the Polls 🍕🇺🇸
unwound.description: We send pizzas to polling places with long lines and other gatherings of civic engagement. Send us reports and we'll send in the reinforcements.
